high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the coffee machine on the counter
Pick up the white mug from the coffee machine
Turn around and walk across the kitchen to the microwave next to the toaster
Heat the mug in the microwave and remove it
Walk back around the kitchen island to the coffee machine
Put the mug in the coffee machine
anns.task_desc: Put the warmed mug in the coffee machine

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the Serve Beverage maker.
Pick up the cup from the Serve machine.
Carry the cup to the Microwave across the kitchen.
Open the microwave door. Set the cup in the microwave on the right part of the plate inside it. Close the door of the microwave. Turn on the microwave.
Open the door of the microwave. Pick up the cup.
Carry the cup across the room to the Serve Beverage maker, set it on the grill in the front of the machine.
anns.task_desc: Take the cup from the beverage machine, carry it to the microwave, cook it in the microwave, return it to the Serve Beverage machine where you originally got it.

high_descs: Turn left, toward the coffee maker at the end of the counter.
Pick up the mug at the coffee maker.
Turn around, go straight, go left and around the counter, then go to the microwave.
Warm the mug in the microwave.
Turn around, turn right, the go straight to return to the coffee maker.
Put the mug at the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm mug at the coffee maker.
